1
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:51,280
I've been in the palace for so long.

2
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:54,520
Tonight, I finally managed to sneak in here with Jingyuan's help.

3
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,880
Si Xingxuan.

4
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,120
You tyrant.

5
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,920
You slaughtered my entire clan

6
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,600
and killed my parents.

7
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:27,920
I won't let you live past tonight.

8
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:40,080
Rumor has it he's temperamental,

9
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,080
bloodthirsty, ruthless,

10
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,289
and kills without blinking an eye.

11
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,530
Capable of any evil.

12
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:53,600
Why does it seem to me

13
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,720
that he falls a bit short of that?

14
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,880
I am the best. Not bad.

15
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,320
Not bad.

16
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:27,400
Give you a CD from the past,

17
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:32,000
to listen to our love back then.

18
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,760
Sometimes it suddenly...

19
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,120
No, no.

20
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,930
If you keep singing,

21
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,220
I won't be able to control myself.

22
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,680
Your Majesty is amazing.

23
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,120
Exactly.

24
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,400
Right, right.

25
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,840
Oh my god.

26
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:56,400
What kind of world have I come to?

27
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,240
It seems

28
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,640
I need to get more familiar with this world.

29
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:52,960
Your Majesty, the meal is ready.

30
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,960
It will get cold if you don't eat now.

31
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,840
Your Majesty.

32
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:03,800
This is your favorite Hibiscus Ruby Tomato Soup.

33
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:07,200
I specially asked the imperial kitchen to prepare it for you.

34
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,280
When did I say I loved it?

35
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,720
Your Majesty, I...

36
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,920
Then tell me.

37
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,360
Which woman do I like?

38
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,160
And which place do I like to go to?

39
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,440
Your Majesty, I didn't mean it.

40
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,840
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

41
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,760
So temperamental.

42
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,200
Do you think you can read my mind?

43
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,420
Why should Your Majesty be upset?

44
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:35,480
Just kill the disobedient ones.

45
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,780
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

46
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,680
Eunuch Sun isn't a good person either.

47
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:43,680
He tells the emperor to kill people at the drop of a hat.

48
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:46,560
Eunuch Sun, you really understand me.

49
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,600
You may all leave.

50
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,360
Leave at once.

51
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:02,040
No, I haven't taken my revenge yet.

52
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,890
I can't miss the opportunity tonight.

53
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,240
I am going to kill you.

54
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:28,560
Why are you not afraid of me?

55
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,960
Such a good opportunity.

56
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,840
It's a pity I don't have a knife.

57
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:32,960
I'm asking you.

58
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,930
Why are you not afraid of me?

59
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:38,280
Your Majesty.

60
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,100
Your Majesty is the Son of Heaven.

61
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,690
The Son of Heaven loves his people.

62
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,000
I am your people.

63
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,940
Why should I be afraid?

64
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,520
Interesting.

65
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,200
Since you are not afraid of me,

66
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:02,720
how about I promote you to a ninth-grade maid

67
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,960
to stay by my side?

68
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,740
He is definitely up to no good.

69
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,520
Your servant, Cangyue,

70
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,720
thanks Your Majesty.

71
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,960
Hey. Don't push.

72
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:31,160
Only three viewing spots are open a day.

73
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,960
Viewing time is limited.

74
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,280
This much. I was here first.

75
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,960
Mine, mine, mine, mine.

76
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:40,000
Hey, let's go.

77
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,760
Come earlier next time.

78
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,680
I am the best.

79
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,480
Your Majesty is amazing.

80
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,880
I love it.

81
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,280
Sold out.

82
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:48,200
What are you looking at?

83
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:51,300
His Majesty is practicing martial arts inside.

84
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,900
Practicing martial arts?

85
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:57,360
He is simply extraordinary.

86
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,720
So majestic.

87
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:02,120
Truly magnificent.

88
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:05,360
You like His Majesty?

89
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,560
Aren't you afraid of death?

90
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,490
What do you know?

91
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:11,200
When His Majesty is happy, he treats us very well.

92
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,640
So what if His Majesty kills people?

93
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,760
Who wants to be a maid forever?

94
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:22,200
Then how many can Your Majesty take on at once?

95
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,320
Five?

96
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,440
Fifty.

97
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,000
Fifty!

98
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:37,159
I can only take on four at a time.

99
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,679
Si Xingxuan alone can take on fifty.

100
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,280
Looks like I'll have to use my wits.
